data.title: Rugrats. Season 1, volume 1
data.meta_description: The Rugrats of the beloved 90s cartoon are back in a brand-new series with an all-new look! Get a knee-high view of the world with this baby band of best friends as they wander off on epic adventures, make new discoveries, and learn about the world and each other, all before snack time! Tommy, Chuckie, Phil, Lil, and Susie may be pint-sized, but their imaginations are larger than life! And they2ll need all that combined brainpower to go up against Tommy2s sneaky cousin Angelica! This volume contains the first thirteen episodes of Season One in a two-disc set!
